  ('heelevel3-10ced7e2-moex-00206', 'heelevel3-10ced7e2', 'heelevel3-10ced7e2-moex-111-b96fcbef', 'sub-heelevel3-10ced7e2-07', NULL, 'essay', '甲出於用球棒打斷乙雙腿、並使其永久失去功能之犯意，某日深夜埋伏
